{"id":1183,"date":"2022-04-01T14:51:33","date_gmt":"2022-04-01T11:51:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=1183"},"modified":"2022-04-01T14:51:33","modified_gmt":"2022-04-01T11:51:33","slug":"visa-rolls-out-nft-creator-program-to-a-global-audience","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/visa-rolls-out-nft-creator-program-to-a-global-audience\/","title":{"rendered":"Visa Rolls Out NFT Creator Program to a Global Audience"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p>Financial powerhouse, <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Visa\">Visa<\/a>, has committed to helping small businesses unlock the potential of NFTs. To achieve this, it is launching the Creator Program in order to provide guidance and mentorship within the industry.<\/p>\n<p>Through the one-year program, Visa intends to <strong>build a global collective of creative pioneers<\/strong> looking to accelerate their businesses through non-fungible tokens. As a result, the team will look to digitally focused artists, musicians, filmmakers and fashion designers to fill out its ranks. First, however, it will undergo a strict vetting procedure to ensure the applicants make the grade.<\/p>\n<p>The Creator Program follows directly on from a similar, yet smaller initiative <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/nftplazas.com\/visa-and-micah-johnson-pair-up-to-support-emerging-artists\/\">launched back in October<\/a>. An innovative scheme that leveraged the talents of former basketballist and current NFT entrepreneur, <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Micah_Johnson3\">Micah Johnson<\/a>. This time around, Micah will return alongside a number of industry experts to take the program globally.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Creators like <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Micah_Johnson3?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Micah_Johnson3<\/a> are at the forefront of NFTs. His work with Visa is an exciting introduction to the Visa Creator Program, a global opportunity for digital creators &amp; artists looking to deepen their understanding of NFT commerce. Learn more: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/oAQknwPdB4\">https:\/\/t.co\/oAQknwPdB4<\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/E6B9QVTyDl\">pic.twitter.com\/E6B9QVTyDl<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Visa (@Visa) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/Visa\/status\/1509123387066617856?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 30, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>Visa estimates that <strong>the digital creator economy now makes over $100 billion annually<\/strong>. Therefore, concluding that NFTs will play a huge part in future growth, as well as representing the next major step in the e-commerce industry. As a result, Visa will look to simplify the purchasing process for digital output by making the buying of NFTs as simple as any other Visa transaction.<\/p>\n<p>To apply for the accelerator program, head over to the Visa website and submit an application. The company will then select the top contenders and make their non-fungible dreams come true.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Apply for the Creator Program &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/globalclient.visa.com\/creator\">Here<\/a> <\/strong><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href